# Next.js Conventions

- Always use Next.js Link from next/link for internal navigation.
  Never use <a href> for internal routes.
- Use next/image for all images.
- Client components that use hooks or browser APIs must include
  'use client' at the top.
- Server components must not include 'use client'.
- Never use localStorage or sessionStorage.
  Authentication state must come from Supabase session.
- All API calls must go through /app/api/ routes.
- Client components must never call Supabase directly.
- Public environment variables must use the NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix.
- Secret environment variables must never use the NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix.
